name: Nothing to jump
description:
You ‘Start with nothing’ you can do, not even jump or walk. You regain those abilities after collecting power-ups.

Walk: A/D Arrow Left/Right

Jump: W/Arrow Up/Space

Double Jump: Jump while in the air.

Does not work in Microsoft Edge.

Made with my C++ engine which in part was also in part created during the jam :D

Made during Ludum Dare 45.
